---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Work with Wendy Ting" description="Work with Wendy Ting — integrative oncology naturopath offering calm, personalised cancer support alongside your existing care.">
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <section class="practitioner">
      <div class="container">

        <!-- Practitioner header -->
        <div class="practitioner-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Wendy Ting</div>
            <h1>A calm, integrative approach to cancer care</h1>
            <p>Supporting you through your cancer journey with clarity, care, and a personalised approach that meets you where you are—so you can move forward with greater steadiness and understanding.</p>
            <div class="cta-row">
              <a class="btn primary" href="/booking">Book a consultation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
<img src="/public/Wendy short hair.jpg"/>
          <div class="qualifications-card card" style="min-height: 360px; justify-content:center;">
            <h3>Her Qualifications</h3>
            <ul class="clean">
              <li>Degree-qualified Naturopath and Medical Herbalist</li>
              <li>Certified Terrain Advocate, Metabolic Institute of Health (Dr Nasha Winters)</li>
              <li>Certified Radical Remission Coach &amp; Workshop Instructor</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Story blocks -->
        <div class="stack-grid">
          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>A comprehensive, integrative approach</h3>
            <p>Wendy is a qualified naturopath and medical herbalist, and in her practice, she embraces a comprehensive, integrative approach to cancer care that addresses the whole person, not just the disease.</p>
            <p>Her method combines several key elements to support profound healing and restore balance, while keeping care thoughtful, grounded, and individualised.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>Deep nutrition. Targeted support.</h3>
            <p>Wendy focuses on deep nutrition, incorporating metabolically healthy foods to enhance overall well-being. Through comprehensive lab assessments, she identifies and corrects imbalances in the body, using targeted herbs and supplements as part of her therapeutic strategy.</p>
            <p>This approach helps to optimise the body's natural healing processes and address the root causes of cancer.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>Holistic care for body, mind and spirit</h3>
            <p>Holistic care is also a crucial part of her practice, including mind-body interventions designed to support emotional and psychological well-being, essential components of the healing journey.</p>
            <p>Wendy employs a framework that integrates evidence-based strategies to empower the body's healing abilities, alongside tailored protocols specific to the type of cancer each patient is facing.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>Personalised plans with clarity and direction</h3>
            <p>Following each consultation, her patients receive a detailed action plan and summary report that outlines their personalised approach to treatment. This ensures that every aspect of care is customised to meet unique needs and supports their journey with precision and care.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-block">
            <h3>A personal note</h3>
            <p>Wendy is an 8+ year Stage IV metastatic breast cancer thriver.</p>
            <p>This journey has shaped her understanding of what it truly means to heal—physically, emotionally and spiritually—and deepened her commitment to supporting others with compassion, clarity and real-world experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Band -->
    <section class="cta-band">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>You don't have to navigate this alone.</h2>
        <p>Book a consultation with Wendy to begin your integrative oncology journey.</p>
        <div class="cta-row" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/booking">Book a consultation</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/contact">Get in touch first</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
